    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in total showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, and there\u2019s not a single scratch or ding to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
